              ],
              "free_text": [
                "A 115 mum thick annular surface barrier detector",
                "was mounted 16 cm from the target so that it subtended",
                "detection angles in the laboratory coordinate system",
                "ranging from 177.5 to 178.9 degrees to the incident",
                "beam direction. In addition, 100 mum  thick",
                "surface barrier detectors were mounted 18 cm from",
                "the target at mean laboratory angles of 160,140,and 120",
                "degrees."
              ]
            }
