          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Energy-averaged four-point angular distribution is",
                "given.",
                "After subtraction of linear backgrounds,peak areas were",
                "extracted for alpha-particle groups corresponding to",
                "particular levels in 32S and were then summed over all",
                "bombarding energies.At some energies and angles certain",
                "groups were obscured by contaminant peaks from 12C, 13C",
                "14N, and 16O in the target. In this cases allowance was",
                "made in the summation over all incident energies by",
                "normalizing all the summed yields to the same total",
                "integrated beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
